3:
But may the righteous people be joyful;\q2 may they rejoice when they are in God's presence;
\q2 may they be happy and very joyful.



\q1

4:
Sing to God; sing to praise him;\q1 sing a song for him who rides in the desert plains;
\q1 his name is Yahweh; be glad when you are in his presence.
